{"tid":561823,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018DSE] 今次請自修中文o既巴絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2018-02-15T10:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T09:26:57.000Z","uid":125535,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f41932c443078fca88a4e90bd5892bbc798909a7","tid":561823,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"之前搞咗幾次講座，反應熱烈，多謝各位支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次又有中文卷一o既自修講座啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位自修中文既巴絲打應該知道, 卷一開始有範文要讀, 自修生究竟要注意D咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n駛唔駛背晒? 邊D係重點? 會有咩題型? <br />\n<br />\n講座內容大概會係:<br />\n1. 文言文要成篇背？<br />\n2. 文言文題型又係乜東？<br />\n3. 最後關頭點溫文言文？<br />\n4. 如何速讀文言文？<br />\n<br />\n誠邀位自修中文既巴絲打一齊黎聽下<br />\n今次請到<span style=\"color: red;\">前日校老師，現職補習社導師，以及有擔任公開試評卷員</span>來做講座，同大家分享文言文技巧。<br />\n<br />\n日期: 28/2/2017 (星期六)<br />\n時間: 6:30-9:00PM<br />\n地點: 太子<br />\n名額: 20人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/LBpCGfLYdDLADbx73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FLBpCGfLYdDLADbx73&d=zgoUwc1%2BETFulaXEfSmDIqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a57c35a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/LBpCGfLYdDLADbx73</a>"},{"pid":"aa42d3a9ca0e09918ab277f1125bb09a80946ed9","tid":561823,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n免費正嘢益大家，真係自己諗起都覺得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d8633dc1dd27c5125f3f6363adcf1be4e02047","tid":561823,"uid":161352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"真係有人去？"},{"pid":"0871962468f731f8a52620e9b71381dcda3af467","tid":561823,"uid":12553